RUN -
Open with Live Server

Runs at port - 
https://localhost:8080

Rules - 
1. Always format the code before commiting.
2. Close resources you have opened. For example - 
dbConnection.close()
3. Naming Convention - CamelCase
4. Remove unused variables.

Clean code guidelines -
1. Always use constants for hard-coded values. For example - 
HELLO_TEAM = "Hello Team!"
2. Class Name - DbConnection - initials capital
3. Function Name - getTodos - first initial small, rest capital